<table border="0" cellpadding="5" width="550" cellspacing="5" height="400" >
<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>I hope you are well.<br></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Further to my email of the <i>(insert date)</i> and email sent on (<i>insert date)</i>.<br></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Please could you let me know if you still wish to make a claim and please do not hesitate to ask if you require any assistance in collecting the information so that we may present a claim.<br></span><br><i style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">(For PI do not reference to still wishing to make a claim as all PI claims need referring to insurers.)<br></i><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">If you no longer wish to make a claim, please could you also reply by return to let me know.<br></span></font><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>I would like to draw your attention to the condition in your policy below:<br></span><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt=""><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br><br>I look forward to hearing from you.<br></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Claims Team<br></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: claims@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>